Our materialized KB is based on a closed-source LLM that does not come with guarantees regarding persistent servicing, and in the past, similar services have been discontinued, hence, long-term reproducibility is not guaranteed. At the same time, our resource therefore has especial archival value. An execution based on an open model is planned.